text: Sergey Smirnov (born 19 January 1961) is a Soviet rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
